{"type":"text","timestamp":1775877733354,"sessionID":"ses_2857184e3ffe6rSn7qG9kyr1b5","part":{"id":"prt_d7a8f7ac4001Vxvo5mrjrgOUtr","messageID":"msg_d7a8f68b0001CHn3FxhS1Kyq06","sessionID":"ses_2857184e3ffe6rSn7qG9kyr1b5","type":"text","text":"## Summary for AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient\n\n### ✅ What Was Completed\n\n**Core Implementation:**\n- `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` - Main `CodeInterpreterClient` class (230 lines)\n- `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` - Data plane client (282 lines)\n- `agentcube/exceptions.py` - Exception hierarchy (4 custom exception classes)\n- `agentcube/utils/` - Supporting utilities for logging and session management\n\n**Implemented Features:**\n- Session lifecycle management (create, reuse existing, delete)\n- Command execution via `execute_command()`\n- Code execution via `run_code()` (supports python/py/python3)\n- File operations: write, upload, download, list\n- Context manager support (`with` statement)\n- Verbose logging mode\n- Router URL configuration (via parameter or `ROUTER_URL` env var)\n- Data plane client with HTTP request handling\n- Session ID routing header (`x-agentcube-session-id`)\n\n**Testing:**\n- `tests/test_code_interpreter_client.py` - 23 tests (293 lines)\n- `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane_client.py` - 24 tests (248 lines)\n- Comprehensive test coverage for initialization, operations, error handling, and edge cases\n\n### ❌ What Was Deferred\n\n**From Original Design Spec:**\n- **Pydantic models** - No `Session`, `ExecutionResult`, `ExecutionJob` models were created; implementation uses raw dictionaries\n- **Async API** - All methods are synchronous; original design called for async methods\n- **SessionStatus/ExecutionStatus enums** - Not implemented\n- **HTTP client wrapper** - Used `requests` directly instead of `httpx` as specified\n- **Retry logic** - Not implemented (original design specified automatic retry for transient errors)\n- **Session listing** - `list_sessions()` not implemented\n- **Individual session retrieval** - `get_session()` not implemented\n- **Asynchronous code execution** - `execute_code_async()` not implemented\n- **Result streaming** - Not implemented\n- **WebSocket support** - Not implemented\n- **Error hierarchy** - Only 4 exception classes instead of the full hierarchy specified (AuthenticationError, ConnectionError, SessionError with subclasses, ExecutionError with subclasses, ValidationError)\n\n**Documentation & Packaging:**\n- No `README.md` for the SDK\n- No API documentation\n- No example scripts\n- No `pyproject.toml` for package distribution\n- Package not publishable to PyPI\n\n**API Differences:**\n- Original design: `CodeInterpreterClient(base_url, api_key)`\n- Actual implementation: `CodeInterpreterClient(name, namespace, ttl, workload_manager_url, router_url, auth_token, verbose, session_id)`\n\n**Estimate Variance:**\n- Original plan: 89 tasks estimated at 15-25 hours\n- Actual implementation: Focused on core functionality, bypassed extensive Pydantic models, async API, and comprehensive error handling","time":{"start":1775877733351,"end":1775877733351}}}
